    {
      "id": "m0000000-0000-4aaa-8aaa-000000000001",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "💰 Monetization Doctrine",
      "position": {
        "x": 720,
        "y": -140
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Monetization Doctrine\n\nTwilite must **capture value without capturing minds**.\n\nThis graph defines *where monetization is allowed*, *where it is forbidden*, and *how value compounds without breaking trust*.",
