    {
      "id": "m0000000-0000-4eee-8eee-000000000010",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🧪 Litmus Test",
      "position": {
        "x": 778.3333333333333,
        "y": 1220
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 200,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Litmus Test\n\n**If this feature vanished tomorrow, would users still own their thinking?**\n\n- Yes → Safe to monetize\n- No → Do not ship\n\nCharge for leverage. Never charge for memory, continuity, or existence.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
